p: U.S. Dist Court 2d Jud Dist W.T.
Catharine L. Martine vs Jesse Martin
Writ of Habeas Corpus for Mary M. Martin
I hereby appoint John Nills of Thurston County to serve the within process for me
JH Kellett Sheriff of Thurston County W.T.

The within come to hand on the 2d day of March 1868 and on the 3d day of said Month I served the same upon the within named Jessee Martin at the house of James Tusnario Thurston County W.T. by reading the contents of the same to him
J H Kellett Sheriff of Thurston Co W.T.
Served By John T. Nills deputy
